--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Release Note for VIVIECR ver.1.2.1.6 (English version)
Release Date: 2010-Aug-23
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This is a maintenance release with enhanced functions for VIVIPOS Application (VIVIECR) 1.2.1.x series.
Previous 1.2.1.x releases may be upgraded to this release by installing the XPI file through Add-ons Manager.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Dependencies
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This release requires the following applications:
    - VIVIPOS OS Release 1.2.2 or above
    - VIVIPOS App Engine Release 1.2.1.5 or above
    - VIVIPOS WebApp and WebServices Release 1.2.1.1 or above

You should also install appropriate language pack (langpack-en-US_1.2.1.6.xpi) to avoid translation-related issues.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Enhanced Functions
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Ticket#138:
Enhance the way data written to the file system: Change the synchronous mode from NORMAL to FULL, to ensure that the data can be immediately and correctly written to the file system.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Bugs Fixed
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Ticket#140:
In the circumstance that 2nd screen function is activated, some screens (eg: Shift Change / End Sale Period screen, Recall Stored Order screen) will be wrongly opened in the 2nd screen.
This issue has been fixed in 1.2.1.6 release.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

